name: Experiment Or Die #37
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Some might say I'm a bit of a hoarder because I collect and save just about anything I think could be used for a creative purpose. One of my favorite designers when I was in school was David Carson and todays piece is a small homage to him. Some of todays assets were sourced from an old magazine he was Art Director for called Raygun. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
